<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.1.6">
<l>pollā vaṭivuṭaip pēyccituñcap puṇarmulai vāymaṭukka</l>
<l>vallāṉai māmaṇi vaṇṇaṉai maruvumiṭam nāṭutirēl</l>
<l>pallā yiramperun tēvimāro ṭupauvamē ṟituvarai</l>
<l>yellāruñ cūḻacciṅ kācaṉattē yiruntāṉaik kaṇṭāruḷar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you are seeking the place where appears</l>
<l rend="indent">the dark jewel hued one who placed his mouth</l>
<l rend="indent">to the breast of the demoness of evil form</l>
<l rend="indent">and was able to drink so that [she] died,</l>
<l>there are those who saw him seated on the lion throne</l>
<l rend="indent">in Dvarakā while the ocean rose,</l>
<l>and all others, along with many thousands of great goddesses,</l>
<l rend="indent"> surrounded [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
